video.title: Quantum Computing and AI
video.description:
Quantum Computers are approaching a turning point where it is starting to bring values to other industries, and one of the first seems to be AI and Machine Learning.
How will the advancements in qubits, algorithms, quantum gates, coherence, error checking, ion trapping, annealing, and superconducting help AI and our industry?
